{"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllControlItemComponentTokensProvider","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/19OUDSTokensComponent011ControlItemB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8CopyableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/TokensProvider"],"type":"conformsTo"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemecontrolitemcomponenttokensprovider"]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"overview","text":"Overview","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for control-item-layout-based component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomControlItemComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the control-item-layout-based component tokens you want.","","        override var sizeMinHeight: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens._500 }","","        override var colorBgFocus: MultipleColorSemanticToken { colors.contentDefault }","","        override var spaceRowGap: SpaceSemanticToken { spaces.paddingInlineTall }","","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomControlItemComponentTokensProvider: ControlItemComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement hundreds of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to give semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then, you can give this "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomControlItemComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" to your own theme implementation:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(controlItem: CustomControlItemComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"or to an already existing theme for example:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    OrangeTheme(controlItem: CustomControlItemComponentTokensProvider())"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider for sizes","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeBorderSemanticTokensProvider for borders","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeColorSemanticTokensProvider for colors","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider for spaces","    let controlItemComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own size, color and space semantic tokens providers (or only some)","    let controlItemComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeControlItemComponentTokensProvider(","                                                sizes: CustomSizeSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                borders: CustomBorderSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                colors: CustomColorSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                space: CustomSpaceSemanticTokensProvider())"]},{"name":"Since","style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"0.10.0","type":"text"}]}],"type":"aside"}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"role"